  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rebuild School for 138 children in Thailand</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Yaowawit School, Farm and Lodge were badly damaged by the heavy rains, floods, and landslides. This devastation has disrupted our school activities and the lives of 138 children and 15 teachers. The three buildings of our school, dormitories and learning facilities are in need of an urgent rebuilding and restoration in order to resume our education services.  With your generosity, we will be able to fix the damage to the school and restore comfort to the lives of our children.</narrative>
  </description>
